Other years in music[edit]

Decades from 1000 to 1300 are redirected to their corresponding centuries in music; centuries from 2000 BC to 1000 AD are redirected to their corresponding millennia:

13th century in music – 12th century in music
11th Century in music – 1st millennium in music
1st millennium BC in music – 2nd millennium BC in music
